creator: Wegow Musica
descriptionHtml:
With Wegow you'll never miss a concert again; is very simple, tell us what music do you like, create your own community and get ready to enjoy live music as always you’ve imagined. Our free app lets you discover people with your same musical tastes, check who has got the ticket and purchase yours.

Get updates from your favourite artists
Synch! select your favorite music genres and artists, we will automatically add them to your profile and notify you when they go to touch to your city. We will also send you notifications based on your music tastes.

Your concert planner wherever you go
Track by genre, city, venue or date. Make different searches and you’ll got in your hand every concert available. If you are travelling, Wegow travels with you, just pop up the app and you will have every concert from the city you are visiting.

Your concert planner wherever you go
Track by genre, city, venue or date. Make different searches and you’ll got in your hand every concert available. If you are travelling, Wegow travels with you, just pop up the app and you will have every concert from the city you are visiting.


Purchase your ticket and... There we go!
The ticket aggregator will show you the best available tickets in real time so you can always take the best available ticket! Are you in?

title: Wegow Concerts

creator: Wegow Musica
descriptionHtml:
With Wegow you will never miss another gig!
Choose the sort of music you like, create your own community and get ready to enjoy live music like you've never imagined. With Wegow’s free app, you’ll be the first to know about all gigs from your favourite artists. You’ll also have a gig calendar that’s tailored to your tastes and always at your hand so you can make the best plans with your friends. Wegow is your one-stop-shop for all concerts!.

- We’ll notify you when your favorite artists come to your city
Sync Wegow with your Spotify account, or select your favorite genres and artists manually - we'll let you know when they're playing in your city.

- Your gig calendar wherever you go
Filter by genre, city, venue or date. Find your gig whatever your taste! If you’re on a trip Wegow will follow you, just open the app and you’ll have the gig calendar for any city you’re in.

- Create your own musical community
Follow your friends, find out which shows they want to go to and join them. Create groups, chat and make plans. You’ll never miss another gig for not having who to go with!

- Buy your tickets
We’ll show you the best available tickets in real time. Choose the best option and we’ll save your ticket in the app! We’re going, are you in?
